## ✅ INSTALLATION CHECKLIST

### Phase 1: Copy Files (10 min)
- [ ] Download all files from /outputs
- [ ] Create `email-templates/` folder
- [ ] Copy .js files to `functions/`
- [ ] Copy .html files to `email-templates/`
- [ ] Copy .jsx file to `src/components/`
- [ ] Copy .md files to root or `docs/`

### Phase 2: Dependencies (5 min)
- [ ] `cd functions`
- [ ] `npm install @sendgrid/mail openai puppeteer`

### Phase 3: Configuration (10 min)
- [ ] Set up SendGrid account
- [ ] Get API key
- [ ] Configure Firebase environment variables
- [ ] Update `functions/index.js`

### Phase 4: Deploy (5 min)
- [ ] `firebase deploy --only functions`
- [ ] `npm run build`
- [ ] `firebase deploy --only hosting`

### Phase 5: Test (10 min)
- [ ] Create test contact
- [ ] Verify email received
- [ ] Check dashboard loads
- [ ] Test manual send

**Total Time:** 40 minutes! 🚀

---

## 🔧 DEPENDENCIES TO INSTALL

Add to `functions/package.json`:

```json
{
  "dependencies": {
    "@sendgrid/mail": "^7.7.0",
    "openai": "^4.20.0",
    "puppeteer": "^21.5.0"
  }
}
```

Then run:
```bash
cd functions
npm install
```

